cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image inpainting, which is a computer vision task, and proposes a learning-based approach using deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of heuristics and techniques to guide the texture transfer, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep neural networks for modeling the task falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on several public datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
